lyrics:
[verse]
Sibusiso, amasondo ajikeleza, inkululeko enhliziyweni yakhe
Emigwaqweni ye-Orange Farm, uhambo lwakhe luqala
Egibela ngaphansi kwezulu elibanzi, amaphupho emehlweni akhe
Kuzo zonke iziphethu, zonke izintaba, umoya wakhe uyaphaphama

[chorus]
Nomoya ebusweni bakhe, nokufudumala kokugona kwelanga
USibusiso ugibela, eqopha izindlela ngokushesha kwakhe
Enhliziyweni ye-Orange Farm, lapho amathemba egxilile
Ebhayisikilini lakhe, uthola injabulo, umuzwa omuhle kangaka
